quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  53,45,aur yeh ke wohi nar aur madah do qisam ( ke hewan ) peda karta hai
  53,46,( yani ) nutfay se jo ( reham mein ) dala jata hai
  53,47,aur yeh ke ( qayamat ko ) isi par dobarah uthana lazim hai
  53,48,aur yeh ke wohi doulat mand banata aur muflis karta hai
  53,49,aur yeh ke wohi sheri ka maalik hai
  53,50,aur yeh ke isi ne Aad awwal ko halaak kar dala
  53,51,aur smod ko bhi. gharz kisi ko baqi nah chorra
  53,52,aur un se pehlay qoum Nooh ko bhi. kuch shak nahi ke woh log barray hi zalim aur barray hi sarkash they
  53,53,aur isi ne ulti hui bustiyon ko day patka
  53,54,phir un par chaaya jo chaaya
  53,55,to ( ae ensaan ) to apne perwar-digaar ki kon si Nemat par jhagrre ga
  53,56,yeh ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) bhi aglay dar sunanay walon mein se aik dar sunanay walay hain
  53,57,anay wali ( yani qayamat ) qareeb aa pohanchi
  53,58,is ( din ki tklifon ) ko khuda ke siwa koi daur nahi kar sakay ga
  53,59,ae munkareen khuda ) kiya tum is kalaam se taajjub karte ho ?
  53,60,aur hanstay ho aur rotay nahi ?
  53,61,aur tum ghaflat mein par rahay ho
  53,62,to khuda ke agay sajda karo aur ( isi ki ) ibadat karo
  54,1,qayamat qareeb aa pohanchi aur chaand shaqq hogaya
  54,2,aur agar ( kafir ) koi nishani dekhte hain to munh phair letay hain aur kehte hain ke yeh aik hamesha ka jaadoo hai
  54,3,aur unhon ne jhtlaya aur apni khawahishon ki pairwi ki aur har kaam ka waqt muqarrar hai
  54,4,aur un ko aisay halaat ( sabqeen ) poanch chuke hain jin mein Ibrat hai
  54,5,aur kaamil danai ( ki kitaab bhi ) lekin darana un ko kuch faida nahi deta
  54,6,to tum bhi un ki kuch parwa nah karo. jis din bulanay wala un ko aik nakhush cheez ki taraf bulaye ga
